      <abstract>
         <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>WHAT?</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                &systemd; is used to manage system settings and services.
                &systemd; organizes tasks into components called <emphasis>units</emphasis> and groups multiple units into 
                <emphasis>targets</emphasis>.
              </para>
            </listitem>
